ong&gt;&amp;#39;Take Profit&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; prices, then wait for the &lt;strong&gt;MT4 &amp;#39;Take Profit&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; to bring about and close the trade.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;\n		Perform regularly last step until you will fulfill with the results&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;\n		Time to the time period, &amp;nbsp;withdraw profit&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\nul.cir_des{ margin-left: 10px; padding-left: 20px}\nul.cir_des li{ list-style-type: square; margin: 6px 4px}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 02:28:51', NULL, 1, '2013-10-07 10:11:20', '183.83.37.214'),
	(3, 1, 'Trading account forms', 'Trading account forms', 'Trading-account-forms', 'Trading account forms', 'Trading account forms', '&lt;div class=&quot;side_left_nav fl hide &quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=72&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account &amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;Types&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=74&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Forex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Islamic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=79&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account Funding&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=81&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Funds Withdrawal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;side_right_nav fl&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;h1 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;\n			Account Forms&lt;/h1&gt;\n		&lt;ul&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;ul&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/Individual_Account_Form.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Individual Account Form &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/Corporate_Account_Form.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Corporate Account Form &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/Business_Introducer_Request.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Business Introducer Request &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/Internal_Funds_Transfer.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Internal Funds Transfer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/Change_of_Trading_Account_Details.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Change of Trading Account Details&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li&gt;\n						&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/pdfs/ForexRay-Withdrawal_of_Funds_Form.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Withdrawal of Funds Form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\n			&lt;/li&gt;\n		&lt;/ul&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			Note&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			To be able to open, view and print the account documentation and forms, you need to install Acrobat Reader or another PDF viewer.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;', NULL, NULL, '0', '2012-11-21 02:48:25', 1, 1, '2013-10-07 11:24:04', '183.83.37.214'),
	(4, 1, 'Forex   Islamic', 'Forex   Islamic', 'Forex-Islamic', 'Forex   Islamic', 'The Swap-free trading account services are intended for traders who use trading systems that do not take into account the impact of swaps or those clients.', '&lt;div&gt;\n	&lt;!--\n&lt;div class=&quot;side_right_nav fl&quot;&gt; --&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;strong&gt;Forex Islamic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;side_right_nav fl&quot; style=&quot;width:auto;&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					The Swap-free trading account services are intended for traders who use trading systems that do not take into account the impact of swaps or those clients who cannot use swaps owing to their religious beliefs. This determines the secondary name of this type of accounts: &amp;ldquo;Forex Islamic accounts.&amp;rdquo; In transition to the swap-free system, all the remaining trading terms and conditions of accounts remain intact.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					When performing deals using the Swap-free trading account for any currency pair, in transiting the position over midnight the trader does not gain or lose any amount, regardless of the position volume. Even holding on the deal for a long time, the trader can be sure that only the conduct of the exchange rate for the set time interval will affect the result of the deal.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					The Islamic Forex accounts offered by Forex Ray are not the same as the Islamic accounts generally offered by other &amp;lsquo;Forex&amp;rsquo; companies. They differ based on the fact that Forex Ray offers Swap-free trading accounts with no other additional charges, whereas most other companies substitute this fee by widening the spread on Islamic accounts. In order to abide by Islamic religious beliefs, one must not pay interest but if that interest charge is transferred to a different type of fee, it is basically still a charge to cover the interest. This is also referred to as a Swap-fee in disguise. Forex Ray does revert to such practices, again demonstrating that Forex Ray offers fair and ethical trading conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					&lt;strong&gt;Forex Ray Swap Free / Forex Islamic Account Characteristics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;ul&gt;\n					&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image:url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position: 5px 8px;padding-left: 25px; &quot;&gt;\n						No interest/swap charges on overnight positions&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image:url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position: 5px 8px;padding-left: 25px; &quot;&gt;\n						No up-front commissions&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image:url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position: 5px 8px;padding-left: 25px; &quot;&gt;\n						No time constraints.&lt;/li&gt;\n					&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image:url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position: 5px 8px;padding-left: 25px; &quot;&gt;\n						No spread widening&lt;/li&gt;\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\n				&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					How to Open a Swap Free / Forex Islamic Account&lt;/h2&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					The Swap-free option can be chosen as part of the trading account registration in three simple steps: Customers that wish to open a Swap-free Islamic Account (1) will have to open a real live money trading account with Forex Ray, (2) fill out the request for a swap free account and accept the &amp;ldquo;Swap-Free Trading Account Use Agreement&amp;rdquo; set forth therein, and (3) thereafter, return the duly signed and executed request for a Swap-free trading account to us by e-mail (in scanned form) or by fax.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					1. To open a real live money trading account, click on the link: Open a real account with Forex Ray&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					2. To download and fill out the request for a Swap-free trading account and accept the &amp;ldquo;Swap-Free Trading Account Use Agreement&amp;rdquo; set forth therein, click on the link: Download&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					3. Return the duly signed and executed request for a Swap-free trading account and &amp;ldquo;Swap-Free Trading Account Use Agreement&amp;rdquo;, either by e-mail (in scanned form) (click here: backoffice@forexray.com).&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					Once the signed form is received by our accounts department, your live &amp;lsquo;Forex&amp;rsquo; trading account will be registered under the Islamic accounts guidelines and the trading policy of your account will be converted to swap-free status.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					Additionally &amp;lsquo;Forex&amp;rsquo; Islamic account holders will be accommodated by a Forex account manager and will be entitled to 24 hour support; please note that if you are a beginner trader you can still download the Metatrader terminal and experience and learn trading with a Forex demo account with no obligations and no questions asked.&lt;/p&gt;\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n					If you have any questions regarding &amp;lsquo;Forex&amp;rsquo; Islamic accounts options please feel free to contact Forex Ray&amp;rsquo;s customer support to clarify any questions or queries you may have.&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 02:51:21', 1, 1, '2014-03-17 10:34:36', '183.83.37.214'),
	(5, 1, 'Account Funding', 'Account Funding', 'Account-Funding', 'Account Funding', 'Account Funding', '&lt;div class=&quot;side_left_nav fl hide &quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=72&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account &amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;Types&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=74&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Forex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Islamic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=79&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account F&lt;/a&gt;orms&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=81&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Funds Withdrawal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;side_right_nav fl&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;h1 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;\n			Account Funding&lt;/h1&gt;\n		&lt;ul&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#minimum&quot;&gt;What is the Minimum Deposit?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#safe&quot;&gt;Is depositing safe and secure?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#cards&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Credit Cards&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#neteller&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Neteller&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#moneybookers&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Moneybookers &amp;ndash; Skrill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#liberty&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Liberty Reserve&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#wire&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Wire Transfer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#Western_Union&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by Western Union&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n			&lt;li&gt;\n				&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.trading-point.com/account-funding#MoneyGram&quot;&gt;How to Deposit by MoneyGram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n		&lt;/ul&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			To make a deposit to your forex trading account please login to &lt;a href=&quot;https://my.trading-point.com/member/login&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;My Account&amp;rdquo;&lt;/a&gt; and select &amp;ldquo;Deposit&amp;rdquo; from the menu.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			You will be presented with a variety of payment options. Please choose your preferred method of depositing and complete all necesary steps. Kindly note that in order to transfer any funds you must first have applied for a Real Account.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray &amp;nbsp;does not accept any payments or deposits from a third party. Any funds received from third party accounts will be returned immediately. Our objective is to make your account funding as convenient as possible. We therefore offer you alternative payment options for depositing funds into your account. All electronic methods of payment including Credit Cards, Liberty Reserve, Moneybookers Skrill and Neteller are 100% Automatic and Instant meaning that upon deposit deposited funds will reflect in your trading account instantly provided you have uploaded your documents and your trading account is verified. Uploading of documents can be performed from the &lt;a href=&quot;http://my.trading-point.com/member/login&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;members area&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Deposits via Credit Cards, Neteller, Moneybookers and Liberty Reserve are 100% Instant and Automatic&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Is depositing safe and secure?&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Yes, depositing money to your account is absolutely safe, private and secure. All transactions are communicated using SSL technology, ensuring that your personal information is safe. All transactions processed from the members area are processed through Secure Socket Layer technology therefore ensuring safety and privacy.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Minimum Deposit&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			In Essence there is No Minimum Deposit however system restrictions limit minimum deposit to $5 for all electronic funding means including Credit Cards and Liberty Reserve.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Credit Cards&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray accepts Visa, Visa Electron, Mastercard, Switch and Solo. Once you choose this payment method and enter the payment details you will be redirected to a secure payment page. You will be asked to enter your credit card and personal information following which the payment will be confirmed. If the transaction is successful your account will be credited instantly.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Please note that all payments must come from an account that has the exact same name as the name on your Forex Ray real account. Forex Ray will not accept any deposits from a third party. Please make sure that the name on the credit card is identical to the name on your Forex Ray real account.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Charges&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray does not charge any fees or commission for depositing funds via Credit Card.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Payment Protection and Data Security&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Please note that Forex Ray does not receive and/or store any personal credit card or payment information. All transactions are processed and protected by Level 1 PCI-DSS Certified Independent International Payment Gateways.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Neteller&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Once you choose this payment method and enter the payment details you will be redirected to the Neteller page for the payment.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			You will be asked to login to your Neteller account to confirm the payment. If the transaction is successful your funds will be credited instantly. Please note that all payments must come from an account that has the exact same name as the name on your Forex Ray real account. Forex Ray will not accept any deposits from a third party.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Charges&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray does not charge any fees or commission for depositing funds. However, Neteller charges up to 3.9% + minimum USD 1.00 per transaction*. Consequently, Forex Ray receives the net amount after these fees are deducted.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			On all your deposits, Forex Ray commits to return these fees by crediting your account instantly. If you do not have a Neteller account you may sign up for one in just a few short steps by going to www.neteller.com or you may choose an alternative payment option.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			* Payments received from India will be charged an additional 0.5%.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Please note that all payments must come from an account that has the exact same name as the name on your Forex Ray real account. Forex Ray will not accept any deposits from a third party.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Charges&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray &amp;nbsp;does not charge any fees or commission for depositing funds. However, Moneybookers charges up to 1.9% + EUR 0.29 per transaction. Consequently, Forex Ray&amp;nbsp; receives the net amount after these fees are deducted. On all your deposits, Forex Ray commits to return these fees by crediting your account instantly.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			If you do not have a Moneybookers account you may sign up for one in just a few short steps by going to www.moneybookers.com or you may choose an alternative payment option.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Liberty Reserve&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Once you choose this payment method and enter the payment details you will be redirected to the Liberty Reserve page for the payment. You will be asked to login to your Liberty Reserve account to confirm the payment. If the transaction is successful your funds will be credited into your account instantly. Please note that all payments must come from an account that has the exact same name as the name on your Forex Ray real account. Forex Ray will not accept any deposits from a third party.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Charges&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray does not charge any fees or commission for depositing funds. However, Liberty Reserve charge 1% per transaction. Min 0.01USD &amp;ndash; Max 2.99USD. Consequently, Forex Ray receives the net amount after these fees are deducted.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			On all your deposits, Forex Ray commits to return these fees by crediting your account instantly. If you do not have a Liberty Reserve account you may sign up for one in just a few short steps by going to www.libertyreserve.com or you may choose an alternative option.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Wire Transfer&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			In order to fund your account, please contact your local bank and request for the Wire Transfer to be sent to the beneficiary according to the details outlined. Immediately upon receipt, the designated amount will be added to your account. Please ensure that your bank quotes both your full name and your trading account number in the payment reference (e.g. John Smith &amp;ndash; Trading Account 12345).&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			This will enable us to identify your payment once it reaches our account. The funds that are transferred should come from a bank account which has the exact same beneficial owner (name and/or title) as the one indicated in your account details. Kindly note that funds sent via wire transfer usually take between 1 and 3 working days to be credited to your account.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 sty