eps by going to www.moneybookers.com or you may choose an alternative payment option.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Liberty Reserve&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Once you choose this payment method and enter the payment details you will be redirected to the Liberty Reserve page for the payment. You will be asked to login to your Liberty Reserve account to confirm the payment. If the transaction is successful your funds will be credited into your account instantly. Please note that all payments must come from an account that has the exact same name as the name on your Forex Ray real account. Forex Ray will not accept any deposits from a third party.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Charges&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Forex Ray does not charge any fees or commission for depositing funds. However, Liberty Reserve charges 1% per transaction. Min 0.01USD &amp;ndash; Max 2.99USD. Consequently, Forex Ray receives the net amount after these fees are deducted.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			On all your deposits, Forex Ray commits to return these fees by crediting your account instantly. If you do not have a Liberty Reserve account you may sign up for one in just a few short steps by going to www.libertyreserve.com or you may choose an alternative option.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			Wire Transfer&lt;/h2&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			In order to fund your account, please contact your local bank and request for the Wire Transfer to be sent to the beneficiary according to the details outlined. Immediately upon receipt, the designated amount will be added to your account. Please ensure that your bank quotes both your full name and your trading account number in the payment reference (e.g. John Smith &amp;ndash; Trading Account 12345).&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n			This will enable us to identify your payment once it reaches our account. The funds that are transferred should come from a bank account which has the exact same beneficial owner (name and/or title) as the one indicated in your account details. Kindly note that funds sent via wire transfer usually take between 1 and 3 working days to be credited to your account.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;p&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '0', '2012-11-21 02:56:04', 1, 1, '2013-10-07 10:05:08', '183.83.37.214'),
	(6, 1, 'Funds Withdrawal', 'Funds Withdrawal', 'Funds-Withdrawal', 'Funds Withdrawal', 'Funds Withdrawal', '&lt;div class=&quot;side_left_nav fl hide &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=72&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account &amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;Types&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=74&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Forex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Islamic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=79&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;Account Funding&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/forexray_plugins/forex_feb_20/?page_id=81&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#039;Droid Sans&#039;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;ccount forms&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;side_right_nav fl&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;h1 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;\r\n			Funds Withdrawal&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n		&lt;ul&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;Funds Withdrawal&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n				&lt;ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						How to Withdraw by Credit Cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						How to Withdraw by Neteller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						How to Withdraw by MoneyBookers &amp;ndash; Skrill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						How to Withdraw by Liberty Reserve&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						How to Withdraw by Wire Transfer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					You have the right to withdraw funds from your account at any point in time. To make a withdrawal from your account please login to &amp;ldquo;My Account&amp;rdquo; and click on the &amp;ldquo;Withdrawals&amp;rdquo; button. You will be presented with a variety of withdrawal options.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Please choose your preferred method of withdrawing funds and insert the amount to withdraw. Kindly note that in order to withdraw funds from your account, Forex Ray must have first received the necessary Identification documents inclusive of Proof of Identity documentation and Proof of Residency documentation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Withdrawal by Wire transfer&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					In order to transfer funds from your Forex Ray account into your bank account, the following information should be provided&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Recipient (Account name)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Bank&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Branch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Account #&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						SWIFT Code&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						IBAN&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If you have not provided the Company with the required information please complete the withdrawal form, scan and send it by email to backoffice@forexray.com.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					You will normally receive the funds in your account within three business days.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Withdrawal to your Credit Card&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If a deposit transaction was made by credit card, withdrawals can be credited to the same credit card. You will normally receive the credit on your account within 2 -5 business days.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Important Note&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Credit Cards which do not belong to the EFT Program your card will not permit Forex Ray to withdraw amounts of funds that exceed initial deposit. In the case that your withdrawal exceeds your initial deposit amounts exceeding that amount will be transferred to you by Wire Transfer. In all cases our back office officer will assist you in making the process of withdrawing your funds as easy and flawless as possible, therefore ensuring quality of service.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Payment Protection and Data Security&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Please note that Forex Ray does not receive and/or store any personal credit card or payment information. All transactions are processed and protected by Level 1 PCI-DSS Certified Independent International Payment Gateways.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Withdrawal to your Neteller Account&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If a deposit transaction was made by Neteller, withdrawals can be credited to the same Neteller account. You will normally receive the funds in your account within one business day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Withdrawal to your MoneyBookers &amp;ndash; Skrill Account&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If a deposit transaction was made by MoneyBookers, withdrawals can be credited to the same MoneyBookers account. You will normally receive the funds in your account within one business day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Withdrawal to your Liberty Reserve Account&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If a deposit transaction was made by Liberty Reserve, withdrawals can be credited to the same Liberty Reserve account. You will normally receive the funds in your account within one business day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Kindly note that&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					In order to protect all parties against fraud, Forex Ray will in most circumstances, only pay funds back to the source of the original deposit. The client shall request to withdraw funds from the trading account in the deposit currency. If the deposit currency differs from the currency of the transfer the amount of the transfer shall be converted by the company into the currency of the transfer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:00:57', 1, 1, '2013-03-13 05:50:45', '127.0.0.1'),
	(7, 1, 'Money Laundering', 'Money Laundering', 'Money-Laundering', 'Money Laundering', 'Money Laundering', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;General statement on Anti-Money Laundering (AML)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Swear Capital Inc is firmly committed to participating in international efforts to combat money laundering and the funding of terrorist and criminal activities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Swear Capital Inc is a Seychelles Company located in Mahe.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Swear Capital Inc implements an AML program that is governed by its Anti-Money Laundering Policy and includes the following AML principles:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Written policies and procedures&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		The appointment of a designated Money Laundering Reporting Officer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Establishing the identification of all relevant clients&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Reporting suspicions transactions&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Retention of relevant records&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Regular staff training&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Conducting business with &amp;acirc;??shell&amp;acirc;?? banks precluded (as defined within the FATF 40 recommendations)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Independent compliance department to review AML programmes as well as&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		External reviews by the regulators/external auditors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:02:26', 1, 1, '2012-11-21 03:03:41', '127.0.0.1'),
