	(9, 1, 'Privacy Policy', 'Privacy Policy', 'Privacy-Policy', 'Privacy Policy', 'This privacy policy units away how Forexray Markets Ltd (&ldquo;FM&rdquo;) utilizes and safeguards any details that you share with FM by using this website.', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Level of Privacy Policy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		This privacy policy units away how Forexray Markets Ltd (&amp;ldquo;FM&amp;rdquo;) utilizes and safeguards any details that you share with FM by using this website.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM is dedicated to making sure that your privacy is safe and protected. Should FM request you to provide particular information by which you can be recognized when utilizing this website, then you can be certain that it will simply be used in accordance with this privacy statement.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM may possibly change this policy from day to day by modernizing this web page. You can examine this webpage from time to time to make sure that you are joyful with any adjustments. This policy is effective from 21/02/12.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;What FM collects&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM just collects personal information when you purposefully provide it to FM, this particular data may include:&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Your own name&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Contact details including e-mail address, mobile phone number and also current address&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Group information such as postcode, personal preferences and interests&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Jobs and also income information&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Additional information related to customer studies and/or offers.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;What FM does indeed with the data collected&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM needs this information to understand your requirements to provide you with a much better service, especially for the following reasons:&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Internal document maintaining.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; FM might use the information to increase our products and services.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; FM may regularly send marketing emails about new services, special deals or other information which we think you might find interesting utilizing the e-mail address which you&amp;#39;ve provided.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;bull; Coming from time to time, FM could also utilize your information to communicate with you for marketing requirements. FM may communicate by email, mobile phone, tele-fax or mail.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Security and safety&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM is dedicated to making sure that your information is safe and sound. In order to reduce illegal access or disclosure, we&amp;#39;ve executed suitable physical, electronic and managerial methods to protect and safe and sound the information all of us collect online. All of the personal data collected from you on the website, such as names, addresses, are usually saved behind a &amp;quot;firewall&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;How FM employs cookies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		A cookie is a small document which requests permission to be placed on your computer&amp;#39;s hard disk. Once you agree, the file is included and the cookie assists analyze website traffic or lets you know whenever you check out a particular site. Cookies permit web programs to respond to you as a particular person. The web application can customize its operations to your requirements, likes and disapprovals by collecting and keeping in mind information about your needs and wants.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM uses visitors log cookies to recognize which pages are getting utilized. This helps FM to examine data about web page traffic and increase FM&amp;rsquo;s web page in order to tailor it to client requirements. FM only employs this information with regard to statistical evaluation requirements and then the data is removed from the machine.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Generally, cookies help FMs to offer you a much better web page, by allowing FM to keep track of which pages you find helpful and which you usually do not. A cookie does not give any use of your computer or any details about you, other than the data you select to share with FM.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		You are able to select to accept or decrease cookies. Most browsers instantly accept cookies, but you generally change your internet browser setting to drop cookies if you choose. This may prevent you from getting complete advantage of the website.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Hyperlinks to some other Web sites&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM&amp;rsquo;s websites may include links to other web sites of awareness. However, once you have utilized these links to leave our website, you should note that FM doesn&amp;#39;t have any control over that any other website. Consequently, FM can&amp;#39;t be responsible for the security and privacy of any information that you simply provide whilst browsing such sites are not ruled by this privacy statement. You need to exercise caution and look at the privacy statement appropriate to the web page under consideration.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Determining your Personal Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		If you have formerly decided to FM utilizing your personal data for immediate marketing requirements, you may change your mind anytime by writing to or contacting at support@forexray.com&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		FM will not really sell, deliver or rent your personal information to 3rd parties unless of course FM has your approval or are required by law to do this. FM may utilize your personal information to deliver you promotional information regarding 3 RD parties which we think you could find useful if you tell that you wish this to happen.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		If you feel that any information FM is keeping about you is incorrect or unfinished, make sure you write or e-mail to FM as quickly as possible, at support@forexray.com. FM will quickly correct any information discovered to be incorrect. Requests by postal mail could be sent to:&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:08:33', 1, 1, '2014-03-17 06:34:54', '183.83.37.214'),
	(10, 1, 'Risk Warnings', 'Risk Warnings', 'Risk-Warnings', 'Risk Warnings', 'Foreign exchange trading, margin trading and derivative trading can be extremely profitable. However the risks involved are equivalent to any potential for gain', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Risk Disclaimer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Foreign exchange trading, margin trading and derivative trading can be extremely profitable. However the risks involved are equivalent to any potential for gain. This risk disclaimer is meant to inform the user of the potential financial risks of engaging in foreign exchange trading. The transaction of such financial instruments known as Forex or FX and dealt on a trading basis known as &amp;lsquo;spot&amp;rsquo; or &amp;lsquo;forward&amp;rsquo; may contain a substantial degree of risk. Before deciding to undertake any such transactions with Swear Capital Inc (hereafter &amp;ldquo;ForexRay&amp;rdquo;) or indeed with any other entity offering similar services, a user should carefully evaluate whether their financial situation is appropriate.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Trading in foreign exchange may result in substantial loss of funds and/or complete loss of funds and should therefore only be undertaken with capital that the investor may afford to lose (risk capital). The definition of risk capital is funds that are not necessary to the survival or well being of the user. ForexRay strongly recommends that any user considering trading foreign exchange, futures or any of the other products ForexRay may propose or broker, read through and study all the main topics contained in the ForexRay website so that they may obtain a clear and accurate understanding of the risks inherent to FX trading.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Opinions on potential or expected market movements as contained from time to time within the ForexRay website are not to be considered necessarily precise nor timely and due to the public nature of the Internet ForexRay cannot at any time guarantee the accuracy of such information. Our direct telephone dealing desk is maintained from Sunday 22:00 GMT+1 to Friday 22:00 GMT+1 as the only method of communication meant to service our customers, and as such, all calls are monitored and recorded. Whilst e-mail and faxed instructions may constitute part of a specific agreement between ForexRay and a client, such procedures shall be pre-documented and agreed upon at account opening.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		As a general warning, if you do not appreciate or fully understand the risks involved in foreign exchange trading, do not open an account.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Please note that the provision of Spot FX products and services does not require licensing, authorization, or registration with the Central Bank of Seychelles and, as a result, it is not covered by the Central Bank of Seychelles&amp;rsquo;s requirements designed to protect consumers or by a statutory compensation scheme. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		If you need clarification you can contact us at &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;sales@forexray.com&lt;/span&gt; and a ForexRay account executive will fully explain all the inherent risks involved in participating in foreign exchange transactions&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:10:01', 1, 1, '2014-03-17 06:36:39', '183.83.37.214'),
	(11, 1, 'Execution Methodology', 'Execution Methodology', 'Execution-Methodology', 'Execution Methodology', 'Execution Methodology', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;ul class=&quot;list_type&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Market execution&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Just Click and Trade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Trade 4 million per time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Guaranteed fills on take profit and stop loss orders&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			24h dealing room access and customer support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Place orders online or by phone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Execution Quality is one of the most important factors you should consider when you are choosing a Forex company. Being ex-interbank dealers ourselves we realise that inferior execution can turn a profitable trading strategy into a losing one. Tight spreads make no sense when you cannot trade on them. That&amp;#39;s why we do our outmost to provide you with the best execution possible.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Placing Orders&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Orders can be placed any time during trading hours via our trading platform. Our trading software supports market, limit, stop and trailing stop orders. Alternatively you may trade via telephone, speaking directly with one of our dealers. Once you open a position it remains open until the matching closing trade is executed. Open positions are constantly revalue at the current market price, updating your account balance in real time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Guaranteed fills on market orders up to 40 lots (4 million)&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Trade 4 million in one click. If you wish to deal in an amount which is greater than 40 lots, you may either break your trade into smaller&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Guaranteed fills on stop loss and limit orders&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		All stop and limit orders up to 40 lots (4 million) are guaranteed to be filled. We understand that stop loss and limit orders are an important&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Holiday/Weekend execution&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		In the case that market gaps from the Friday close to the Sunday opening, pending Limit or Stop orders will be executed at the first&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Trading during Volatile or Illiquid Markets&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		In volatile market conditions (during market moving news events or particularly active markets) market orders will still be executed at market price if prices haven&amp;acirc;??t moved in the accepted latency times. However, when the price has moved significantly you will be filled at the best available price. This can be in the client&amp;acirc;??s favour or against. Spreads may widen. Forex Ray makes every effort to keep these enlargements as low and rare as possible through its partnerships with multiple liquidity providers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:19:32', 1, 0, '2012-11-22 18:54:31', '127.0.0.1'),
	(12, 1, 'Open Demo', 'Open Demo', 'Open-Demo', 'Open Demo', 'Open Demo', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Please complete the form below to create your Free Demo trading account with ForexRay.&lt;br /&gt;\n		Once you have submitted your details, you will receive an email which contains a link to activate your account,&lt;br /&gt;\n		and you can then begin trading with your practice account immediately.&lt;br /&gt;\n		[contact-form-7 id=&amp;quot;177&amp;quot; title=&amp;quot;Open Demo&amp;quot;]&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:35:48', 1, 1, '2013-03-19 02:08:32', '183.83.52.88'),
	(13, 1, 'Open Live', 'Open Live', 'Open-Live', 'Open Live', 'Open Live', '&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Please complete the form below to create your Live trading account with ForexRay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		You will shortly receive an email with your Login details and instructions on how to make a deposit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		[contact-form-7 id=&amp;quot;185&amp;quot; title=&amp;quot;Open Live&amp;quot;]&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2012-11-21 03:38:54', 1, 1, '2013-03-13 06:14:16', '127.0.0.1'),
