	(67, 1, 'About Forexray', 'About Forexray', 'About-Forexray', 'About Forexray', 'ForexRay  Founded under the name Swear Capital OU  the company rapidly established itself as a leading online forex  broker dealer', '&lt;div class=&quot;pg_data_view&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;post  pad10 newsbox&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;story&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 5, 128); margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					About Forexray:{WIDGET-00022}&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;strong&gt;ForexRay &lt;/strong&gt;Founded under the name Swear Capital OU is registered as a spot forex broker by the Ministry of Economic Affairs (registration nr VVT000306, FRA000040) in Estonia, a member country of European Union and the Eurozone.&amp;nbsp; the company rapidly established itself as a leading online forex&amp;nbsp; broker dealer with a focus on providing high quality brokerage services to individual and corporate and business clients, &amp;nbsp;ForexRay.com is a part of the ForexRay Businesses Group. This can be a group of financial and financial commitment companies which provide online trading services. ForexRay Company is ECN Forex broker. Presently, we have&amp;nbsp;more than 40,000 consumers and corporate customers. Every day more than 50 unique traders&amp;#39; open accounts by using ForexRay to make investments in financial trading markets. A comprehensive range of forex trading choices&amp;nbsp; Forex technical support and advisory services are available to all of our customers, regardless of their funds. All of our specific priority is to provide full-range services and to provide customer stewardship at each and every stage, beginning from new account registration to funds withdrawal.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					In 2012, under the direction of a unique and powerful management team, the company experienced significant change for the better to ForexRay. The change of name was a powerful statement designed to represent the amount of the company had developed and also to more obviously portray the characteristics of the business.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;strong&gt;ForexRay&lt;/strong&gt; trading conditions are well regarded as one of the very best around the world. All of our customers have free access to a great selection of trading instruments as well as two state-of-the art information systems and software products through the top rated companies such as MetaQuotes Software MetaTrader 4 designers), Reuters, e-Signal and many others. To find access to trading options, open ForexRay trading account over the internet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/uploads/Forexray_Business_Profile.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;\r\n    font-size: 16px;\r\n    color: black;&quot;&gt;BUSINESS PROFILE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.forexray.com/uploads/1400698249_1653820821_fxray.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/uploads/1376170138_1795503485_edeal.png&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;About Forexray&quot; src=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/uploads/1376170138_1795503485_edeal.png&quot; style=&quot;width:100%; height: 161px;-webkit-border-radius: 4px; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;border: 1px solid #c9cdd0;margin-bottom:14px;&quot; title=&quot;About-Forexray&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n					Relationship with main market makers and brokers-contractors as well as, a power