	(72, 1, 'Company News', 'Company News', 'Company-News', 'Company News', 'ForexRay  forex trading amount reached a new high of USD 10billion, which can be 11 % increased than the average monthly volume in the first quarter.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY COMPANY NEWS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Dear Consumers, We all keep on growing number of bank accounts for diversification and take much more reliable forex trading banks as our partners.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forex trading amount reached&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Dear Clients Members!&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	ForexRay &amp;nbsp;forex trading amount reached a new high of USD 10billion, which can be 11 % increased than the average monthly volume in the first quarter of 2013.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Company news&quot; title=&quot;Company-News&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376169824_2135591250_edeal.jpg&quot; style=&quot;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;border: 1px solid #c9cdd0; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom:14px;&quot; width=&quot;660&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Notification for Liberty Reserve users&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Dear clients and partners!&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	We inform you that the electronic payment system Liberty Reserve has serious technical problems from 05/24/2013 till the current moment (the official website is not available, the service does not work), that leads to the partial or full blockage of deposit/withdrawal operations from trading accounts of our clients via this payment system.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forexray eliminates commission on transfers through NETELLER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	In order to make payments even more simple and profitable, Forexray team has decided to eliminate commissions on transfers through the NETELLER online payment system.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Now the company&amp;#39;s clients can both deposit and withdraw funds from their accounts without additional charges. Furthermore, fund withdrawals to NETELLER eWallets will be carried out automatically.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Free Analytical Reviews&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	FOREXRAY has signed a contract with Trading Central &amp;ndash; the market leader in financial consulting services. This partnership gives FOREXRAY clients the opportunity to daily receive free technical analysis on leading currency pairs.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The new service gives traders access to research, which has been recognized for its significance by the world&amp;rsquo;s leading financial institutions. FOREXRAY clients will be able to receive technical analysis on the following currency pairs: GBPUSD&amp;nbsp; EURUSD, , USDCHF,...&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 02:44:03', 1, 1, '2014-03-14 07:20:28', '183.83.37.214'),
	(73, 1, 'Testimonials', 'Testimonials', 'Testimonials', 'Testimonials', 'Every day we at Forexray.com get spontaneous notes from our members thanking us and sharing their impressions of the quality of our services.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 5, 128); margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Testimonials:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Every day we at Forexray.com get spontaneous notes from our members thanking us and sharing their impressions of the quality of our services. Below is a sample of hundreds of emails and unsolicited testimonials we receive. We would love to hear your forex trading success.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Testinomial&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376163081_1141133774_edeal.jpg&quot; style=&quot;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;border: 1px solid #c9cdd0;-webkit-border-radius: 4px; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;&quot; title=&quot;Testimonials&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forex Trading Testimonials:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The very best testimonial we have is that lots of traders have been with us for over 6 years! Really few providers can say that. And many of the traders who do leave come back. There is no Holy Grail in the Forex. Traders must learn to trade, FOREXRAY. All of the testimonials below are used with permission from the consumer. Your knowledge could vary and is not indicative of your own trading knowledge. Testimonials are believed to be true depending on the representations of the persons providing the testimonials, but facts stated in the testimonials have not been independently audited or verified. Nor has there been any test to dete