	(83, 1, 'Deposit Funds', 'Deposit Funds', 'Deposit-Funds', 'Deposit Funds', 'Deposit Funds', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 5, 128); margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY- DEPOSIT FUNDS METHOD&amp;#39;s:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Here, you can start an FX trading account, deposit funds to/from already existing FOREXRAY trading accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	To make sure you deposit &amp;nbsp;funds to/from an FOREXRAY trading account, Determine the exact type of procedure. Once you reach the part you need, you will be transferred to a secure transaction area for processing deposits.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	To change FOREXRAY trading account settings, just like leverage size, personalized information, mobile phone password or your current PIN-code, please contact the technical support service using email: support@forexray.com.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	An easy option for making deposits to an FOREXRAY trading account utilizing virtual prepaid cards selected in the national currency of your country.EXCARD - nominal commissions for payment, flexibility in transferring money and quality reliability of all transactions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Electronic and Digital Payment Methods:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY methods deposits &amp;nbsp;utilizing the following payment methods:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;gallery_view o_h&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;gallery_view o_h&quot; style=&quot;overflow: hidden;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;cur_imgs&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 208px; height: 106px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;img class=&quot;cur_img&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376170575_1927598723_edeal.png&quot; width=&quot;86&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;cur_imgs&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 208px; height: 106px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;img class=&quot;cur_img&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.