iv&gt;\n		&lt;div&gt;\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;cur_imgs&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Credit cards:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	People may use Visa and MasterCard to deposit money in your FOREXRAY trading account.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Wire Transfers OR Exchanges:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	People may deposit funds in your FOREXRAY trading account by wire transfer. To produce a wire transfer, utilize the standard bank account details found in your Personal Area.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	More Important! Funds deposited by wire transfer may only be withdrawn to an FOREXRAY account belonging to the customer who made the valid wire transfer.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;How does the deposit?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Depositing funds directly into your trading account is rapidly and straightforward. There are different methods with which you can fund your account, simply just choose whichever method you prefer. In purchase to start trading you need to first create a trading account. Please make sure to follow these steps:&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Register to open an account - click here&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Login to the trading platform&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Click on the &amp;ldquo;Account Balance&amp;rdquo; button showing on the bottom left hand side&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Click on &amp;ldquo;Deposit&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Select your desired deposit method.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Is definitely depositing safe and protected?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p&gt;\n		Yes, depositing funds to your account is absolutely safe and sound, private and secure. All of the transactions are communicated utilizing Secure Socket Layer technologies, providing that your personal information is safe.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:08:44', 1, 1, '2013-09-02 08:51:01', '183.83.2.184'),
	(84, 1, 'Withdraw Funds', 'Withdraw Funds', 'Withdraw-Funds', 'Withdraw Funds', 'Withdraw Funds', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY- WITHDRAW FUNDS METHOD&amp;#39;s:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Here, you can start an FX trading account, Withdraw funds to/from already existing FOREXRAY trading accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	To make sure you Withdraw &amp;nbsp;funds to/from a FOREXRAY trading account, make sure you, determine the exact type of procedure. Once you reach the part you need, you will be transferred to a secure transaction area for processing of Withdraw Funds &amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	To change FOREXRAY trading account settings, just like leverage size, personalized information, mobile phone password or your current PIN-code, please contact the technical support service using email: &lt;b&gt;support@forexray.com.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	An easy option for making Withdraw to a FOREXRAY trading account utilizing virtual prepaid cards selected in the national currency of your country.EXCARD - nominal commissions for payment, flexibility in transferring money and quality reliability of all transactions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Electronic and Digital Payment Methods:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY methods Withdraw Funds &amp;nbsp;utilizing the following payment methods:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;gallery_view o_h&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;cur_imgs&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;img class=&quot;cur_img&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376170575_1927598723_edeal.png&quot; width=&quot;86&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;cur_imgs&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;img class=&quot;cur_img&qu