	(85, 1, 'Forexcopy System', 'Forexcopy System', 'Forexcopy-System', 'Forexcopy System', 'Forexcopy system allows Forexray clients to send money to accounts of some other clients of the company, which significantly performance of Forexray account.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forexcopy System:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Having recognized the Forexcopy Offer Deal in Client Cabinet, each and every Forexray trader has the account automatically registered with a funds transfer system - Forexcopy.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The actual Forexcopy system allows Forexray clients to send money to accounts of some other clients of the company, which significantly broadens the performance of the Forexray account. Therefore, Forexray has been an more yet optional service available to every Forexray account holder in Client Cabinet.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Internal exchanges (transfers between trading accounts) allow Forexcopy clients to extend accounts of friends in just one more! Right this moment every client of Forexray Company is totally free to transfer funds to any other Forexray account holder with the Forexcopy service activated.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The method of Forexcopy activation is very simple and comprises just two steps: -&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Accepting the Forexcopy Offer Agreement; - joining the nickname in the system. Personal information of customers is usually quite faithful to the Forexray system: it just isn&amp;#39;t revealed&amp;nbsp; two receivers and senders of funds.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The particular method of money transfers in between the A/C&amp;#39;s is commission-free. Developed as a means of support for the faithful Forexray clients, the Forexcopy system is a remarkable facility of a modern Forexray trader.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The actual Forexcopy system can also be used for choosing payments between buyers and sellers of Forex alerts and expert advisors. The company works as a powerful intermediary processing internal transactions and guarantees security and safety of transactions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;The Forexcopy system is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;list-style&quot; style=&quot;list-style:none;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Forexray transfers to friends and family members.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;No commission fees and service fees.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Simple Sign up for the system in Forexray Client Cabinet;&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;It is not disclosed even to receivers and senders of funds&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;The best security fee of the operations conducted;&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Handy user interface in Client Cabinet.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;SSL protection of high stability and safety standard.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Anonymous is receiving and sending funds.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Direct interaction with other Forexray accounts.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li class=&quot;list-check&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:none;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;Helpful Forexray Help and support Service.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\nul.list-style li{list-style-type: square}\n.list-style{ margin: 10px 0 10px; padding-left: 36px; }\n.list-check{background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 2px 0px;padding-left: 20px;padding-bottom: 10px;list-style-type:none;}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:16:43', 1, 1, '2014-03-17 10:35:23', '183.83.37.214'),
	(86, 1, 'PAMM', 'PAMM(Percentage Allocation Management Module)', 'PAMM', 'PAMM', 'FOREXRAY Group is pleased to introduce to you the unique program of managed accounts. Managed account (PAMM - Percentage Allocation Management Module).', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 5, 128); margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;PAMM:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forexray.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Group is pleased to introduce to you the unique program of managed accounts. Managed account (PAMM - Percentage Allocation Management Module) is a part of percentage allocation, which allows you to manage investors&amp;#39; funds in an integrated manner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray&amp;nbsp; PAMM system provides an opportunity to make investments in Forex projects. Each and every customer of Forexray Company can easily accept investments from other traders or invest funds in PAMM accounts and turn into a shareholder of this account.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray PAMM system consists of two categories of users:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; Customers who registered their separate accounts with the PAMM system as traders&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; Customers who registered their accounts with the PAMM system as investors&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Investors utilize the technique of PAMM accounts in order to invest their funds in Forexray trader accounts with the purpose of using a piece of the profit made by traders. The process of investing suggests the transfer of funds under the company&amp;#39;s manage which allows an investor to a share in a trading account balanced to the investment.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The PAMM system by Forexray offers all its users to manage and report on all operations, shares and results in an automatic function. A trader can accept an unlimited number of investments of total quantity from an unlimited number of investors.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;PAMM&lt;/strong&gt; stands for the Percentage Allocation Management Module&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	PAMM account is a trading account that includes lots of unconditional Investors&amp;rsquo; accounts, symbolizing an independent and unified trading organization, which is managed only by the Manager (a vendor or company) of the PAMM account.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Several Investors&amp;rsquo; accounts provided in a PAMM account are regarded by the trading platform as an integral whole. The funds from all Traders on the master record are traded as one unit, which gives much more income for funds management and much better capacity control options. Manager&amp;rsquo;s auction results (trades, Profit &amp;amp; Loss) are assigned between Investors&amp;rsquo; accounts according to percentage; PAMM account is a specialized formula that helps to automatize profit/loss distribution, eliminate human error and allows Money Managers to manage multiple Investors&amp;#39; accounts via one focused MT4/MT5 interface.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; Profit allocation alternatively of demand allocation&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; Any kind of business even with small volume effects on all slave accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Simple attaching and detaching of slave accounts at any time&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Unlimited number of traders&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Slave accounts can be in