would like to meet winnings on Forex and CFD markets.', NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:20:16', 1, 1, '2014-03-26 09:25:40', '183.83.37.214'),
	(87, 1, 'Trading Platforms', 'Trading Platforms', 'Trading-Platforms', 'Trading Platforms', 'Trading Platforms', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Automated Trading: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	You can increase your trading opportunities with the &lt;strong&gt;MetaTrader 4 Automated Trading System.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Automated Trading&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376199839_1804932126_edeal.jpg&quot; width=&quot;650&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Mobile Trading: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Stay connected and manage your trading account while on the move. Access financial markets, technical analysis.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Mobile Trading&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376200277_814333581_edeal.gif&quot; width=&quot;650&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Managing Multiple Accounts:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Are you having a hard time managing several trading accounts? MetaTrader 4 MultiTerminal is the ideal solution for you.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:42:11', 1, 1, '2013-10-07 12:07:08', '183.83.37.214'),
	(88, 1, 'Forexray MT4', 'Forexray MT4', 'Forexray-MT4', 'Forexray MT4', 'Forexray MT 4 is a well-liked trading system designed to operate with such financial resources as currency pairs, CFD, and futures trading.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forexray MT4:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Forexray MT 4 is a well-liked trading system designed to operate with such financial resources as currency pairs, CFD, and futures trading. Developed and Designed by MetaQuotes Software Corp., One of the leading&amp;nbsp; software companies, MT4 combines comfort and functionality of high quality software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Meta trader (MT4) Installation or Setup&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;a href=&quot;http://forexray.com/home/metatrader&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Download Meta Trader 4&quot; title=&quot;Download Meta Trader 4&quot; src=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/uploads/1381156111_1382944693_fxray.png&quot; style=&quot;width:220px; height: 70px;-webkit-border-radius: 4px; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;margin-bottom:14px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Right after installation is over or when launching the program for the first time, you will see the login window.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Make use of the username and password you have received in your welcome e-mail after opening a demo or real account to login.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Download The Forexray Metatrader 4 User and Error Guide&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/home/download/Metatrader_4_User_Guide.pdf&quot;&gt;Download The Forexray MetaTrader 4 User Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.forexray.com/home/download/Metatrader_4_Error_Guide.pdf&quot;&gt;Download The Forexray MetaTrader 4 Error Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;MT4 Platform Features and Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Full technical review package: 50+ inbuilt indicators and charting tools&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	The ability to create individual trade indicators, different time periods (from minutes to months)&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Secure and safe transactions sessions: Clients are prepared with a specific username and password&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Online news&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Multi-language system interface&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;History database management and real-time data import/export service&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Signals of the system and trading activities&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Internal mailing system&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Streaming prices in up to 400 lots (40 million)&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Mobile Trading: MetaTrader 4 Mobile for PDA&amp;#39;s and desirable mobile phones&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Built-in help guides for MetaTrader 4 and MetaQuotes Language 4&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Automated trading Program your own techniques using the Expert Advisor&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;System Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	PC with Microsoft Windows 98 SE2 operating system or higher.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Intel Celeron based processor, with a rate of recurrence of 1.7 GHz or higher.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Screen resolution of 1024*768 pixels or higher.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;256 MB of RAM or much more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;50 MB of total available drive space.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Simply click on the link to download MetaTrader 4 for a PC user guide to download the user guide&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	MetaTradeForex, Futures trading, and CFDs on the world&amp;rsquo;sleadingobjectives with Absolutely no Requotes and Absolutely no Rejections. Analyze the markets through ancomplete technical analysis package and streaming market news. Trade manually or set up professional advisors that can automatically place orders for you.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	MT 4 is the most preferred, user friendly and trusted online forex trading platform on the current market today, offering free features to help traders, and money managers make knowledgeable trading choices. For this reason, Forexray has made MT 4 its trading platform of choice and promotes traders to take full advantage of all the fantastic features available.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Trade with various order types&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Analyze the current market with 50+ built-in indicators or expand your own&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Use EAs for automated trading&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;list-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Customize the way to your requirements.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul style=&quot;list-style:none;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;style tyoe=&quot;text/css&quot; type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.list-img-style{text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:48:32', 1, 1, '2014-03-14 07:33:43', '183.83.37.214'),
	(89, 1, 'Forexray MAM', 'Forexray MAM', 'Forexray-MAM', 'Forexray MAM', 'The Forexray MAM has all the features of the standard MT4 interface, including full use of the MT4 charting package, automated trading and expert advisors.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forexray MAM:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The &lt;strong&gt;Forexray MAM&lt;/strong&gt; performs differently from the traditional MetaTraderMultiterminal by allowing for fund managers, portfolio managers and multiple account holders manage multiple MT4 trading accounts at the same time with the use of one account.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The Forexray MAM has all the features of the standard MT4 interface, including full use of the MT4 charting package, automated trading and expert advisors (EA&amp;rsquo;s). The MAM software program enables aeasy way of managing multiple accounts with all commissions built up automatically, making it profitable for fund managers to trade with clients&amp;rsquo; accounts in a transparent way.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Exactly how Forexray MAM Works:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Through the MAM software the Manager&amp;rsquo;s MT4 trading account is assigned as Master Account as well as the Investors&amp;rsquo; accounts, which are managed by the Manager, are recognized as Follower Accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Our MAM software is ideal for managing and trading various MT4 accounts simultaneously. The MT4 MAM is one of the most experienced and flexible platforms in the market today; used by Money Managers and experienced traders equally.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;MAM Following Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n	Supports an unlimited number of MT4 trading accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n	Provides an analysis of available trades, balances and extra levels on numerous accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n	Bulk order execution for immediate assignment to sub accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;entry clearfix post&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		The Trading Point Multi Account Manager Software operates differently from the classic Metatrader Multiterminal by allowing fund managers, portfolio managers and multiple account holders to manage multiple MT4 trading accounts at the same time with the use of one account. The MAM offers all the features of a normal MT4 interface including full usage of the MT4 charting package and full usage of automated trading and MT4 Expert Advisors (EA&amp;acirc;??s). The MAM software enables a simple way of handling multiple accounts with all commissions accrued automatically making it both effective and efficient for fund managers to trade customer accounts transparently.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;How does the MT4 MAM Work?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		The MAM software allows the managers MT4 account to be assigned as Master Account and client accounts which are handled by the manager to be recognized as follower accounts with the total sum of trusted money treated as a whole and traded by the Managers Master Account.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Profits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Profits from closed orders are automatically distributed to original account owners (follower accounts).&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Losses&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Losses from closed orders are distributed among the money that takes part in the trading activity therefore ensuring that a client having his funds handled by a manager never risks more than he agreed to trust to his manager.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Instructions on How To Apply for a MT4 Multi Account Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		1. Both Manager and Investors are required to open a Real Trading Account with Trading Point.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		2. Investors must complete a limited power of attorney, which will provide the manager with the right to trade&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		the funds on their behalf.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		3. Investors must send the signed limited power of attorney to sales@forexray.com.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		4. Manager has the responsibility to contact sales@forexray.com and request that his Real Trading Account has&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		the MAM software enabled and all authorized accounts set manageable by his Master Account.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Important: Please note that Investors can revoke the limited power of attorney at anytime by contacting sales@forexray.com&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Who Can Apply for the MT4 Multi Account Manager Software?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Fund Managers&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Asset Managers&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Multiple Account Holders&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Examples&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Let&amp;#39;s take an example that a Fund Manager has 3 clients so in essence both Account Manager and the 3 clients are all required to open Real Trading Accounts Individually. Please note that when a client registers a Real Account he automatically receives an email with access details which are automatically emailed to the email inbox of email address used upon registration.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;In order to make the example easy we will use hypothetical account numbers below:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Master Account Login number : 1000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 1 Login Number : 1001&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 2 Login Number: 1002&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 3 Login Number: 1003&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		The Master Account cannot make a deposit. If the Fund Manager wants to deposit money then he needs to register another sub account which it will be in his name and therefore a 4th Sub Account will be needed in our example. But let&amp;acirc;??s continue our example with the 1 Master Account and the 3 Sub Accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Login 1001 = Deposits $10000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Login 1002 = Deposits $10000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Login 1003 = Deposits $20000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		So if the 3 Sub Accounts make a deposit the Master Account will see in his Balance the total of all deposits made by the sub accounts under his name which in our case it will show $30000. Now, when the Master Account opens a position it divides that position per equity ration into the Sub Accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Master Account Buys 4 Lots EURUSD at 1.33000 then automatically all Sub Accounts will see&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 1 = Buy 1 Lot EURUSD 1.33000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 2 = Buy 1 Lot EURUSD 1.33000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Sub Account 3 = Buy 2 Lot EURUSD 1.33000&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;When can the Master Account start Trading on behalf of his clients?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		1. Once all accounts are registered and they already received their access details then all Sub Accounts need to sign a Power of Attorney where you can find here.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		2. Second step is that all sub accounts need to fund their trading accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		3. Third step is that the Master account holder needs to provide sales@forexray.com a written email with all login numbers of his clients requesting the MAM and then he/she can start trading.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		4. Once these have been matched to the corresponding power of attorneys from the respective account holders, then all sub accounts will be set under the Master Account.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Quick Steps of using the MAM:&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		1. Registering Real Accounts with&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Nimiety Corp&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		2. Signing the POA(Power of Attorney)&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		3. Funding the accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		4. An email should be send from the Master account with all login numbers of the sub accounts requesting the MAM solution.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		5. You can now start trading.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		The Power of Attorney shall remain valid towards the COMPANY until the day when a revocation of the Power of attorney is provided in written by the Client (Sub Account). At that stage Trading Point is forced to remove the sub account which is until that date handled by the Master account. This in reality means that any positions held by the sub account will be closed and the volume in the position of the Master Account will be partially closed.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Example: A Master Account opens 5 Lots and for various reasons one of the Sub Accounts that received the signal of 1 Lot decides to cancel the power of attorney then that position of 1 Lot in the client&amp;acirc;??s account will be closed and in the Master Account the 5 Lots will become 4 open Lots and 1 Lot closed.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;MAM Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Live P&amp;amp;L data for clients&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Daily/instant reports on individual accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Multiple account management directly from MetaTrader4 Client Terminal&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Unlimited trading accounts&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Different allocation methods&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Full SL/TP functionality&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;li-style-img&quot;&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp; Flexible trading options&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;MT4 MAM Vs Classic Metatrader (MT4) Multiterminal&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		Unlike the usual Metatrader Multiterminal the MT4 Multi Account Manager Software (MAM) allows full and unlimited usage of charts and all EA&amp;acirc;??s as in reality the Master Account is not required to deviate from the MT4 client terminal.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;strong&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Nimiety Corp&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;does not participate in any way in trading decisions made by external Fund Managers and makes no representations, warranties and assumes no obligations with regard to any external Fund Manager&amp;acirc;??s trading strategy and/or performance.&lt;/p&gt;\n	&lt;div&gt;\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.li-style-img{text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 18:57:45', 1, 1, '2014-03-18 11:31:45', '183.83.37.214'),
	(90, 1, 'Forexray iPhone Trader', 'Forexray iPhone Trader', 'Forexray-iPhone-Trader', 'Forexray iPhone Trader', 'Apple iOS (an operating system for the iPhone and iPad) are the most widely-used and preferred mobile platform for both mobile phones and tablet computers.', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forexray iPhone Trader:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Apple iOS (an operating system for the iPhone and iPad) are the most widely-used and preferred mobile platform for both mobile phones and tablet computers. Trading devices for the iPhone and iPad allow traders to understand the current market and benefit from their Android-based mobile phone devices and tablet PCs running on iOS.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Foexray iPhone Trader&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376202506_2041381075_edeal.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Foexray-iPhone-Trader&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Real-time quotes of all financial devices.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Opening and closing any kind of Quick and Market orders: BuyStop, SellStop, Purchase Limit, Sell Limit, StopLoss, TakeProfit.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Real-time live charts with zoom and scroll, 7 time frames, 3 chart types (bars, line charts, Japanese candlesticks).&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	ForexrayForex Trading directly from a chart. Trading levels and volumes are on the chart.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	30 specialized indicators, adjustable graphical options of technical indicators (color, line width)&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Monitoring of open positions account balance and overall trading history.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	ForexrayForex Trade on the go anywhere and anytime with the dedicated iPhone app. The MT4 iPhone program works by using state of the art technology and there are no required to register or provide personal information.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;The MT4 iPhone ForexrayForex trading app provides you the ability to trade with the same capabilities available on the ForexRay MT4 platform.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.p-img-style{text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;}&lt;/style&gt;', 'Forexray iPhone Trader:  	Apple iOS (an operating system for the iPhone and iPad) are the most widely-used and preferred mobile platform for both mobile phones and tablet computers. Trading devices for the iPhone and iPad allow traders to understand the current market and benefit from their Android-based mobile phone devices and tablet PCs running on iOS.  	  	Real-time quotes of all financial devices.  	Opening and closing any kind of Quick and Market orders: BuyStop, SellStop, Purchase Limit, Sell Limit, StopLoss, TakeProfit.  	Real-time live charts with zoom and scroll, 7 time frames, 3 chart types (bars, line charts, Japanese candlesticks).  	ForexrayForex Trading directly from a chart. Trading levels and volumes are on the chart.  	30 specialized indicators, adjustable graphical options of technical indicators (color, line width)  	Monitoring of open positions account balance and overall trading history.  	ForexrayForex Trade on the go anywhere and anytime with the dedicated iPhone app. The MT4 iPhone program works by using state of the art technology and there are no required to register or provide personal information.  	&amp;nbsp;The MT4 iPhone ForexrayForex trading app provides you the ability to trade with the same capabilities available on the ForexRay MT4 platform.', NULL, '1', '2013-03-