	(95, 1, 'Partnership', 'Partnership', 'Partnership', 'Partnership', 'Partnership', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Partnership:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The Forexray Partnership program is your chance to step into a convenience business opportunity on highly helpful terms. It&amp;rsquo;s a chance to make money no substance where you are located and no question of the timing and amount of your clients&amp;rsquo; Forex trades.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray uses a number of methods to determine your rewards, depending on the type of account used by the Client you&amp;rsquo;ve registered. If a Forex Mini account has been opened with your agent&amp;rsquo;s guide then a percentage method is used to work out your Partner gift,&amp;nbsp; You will get a percentage at 20% or more from the growth of investments of each and every of the Customers you have signed up. Down the line, once you have become a Properly introducing Broker for Forexray and introduced in a larger number of Clients you can increase the size of your reward.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;partnership&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376204127_1365503400_edeal.gif&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-border-radius: 4px; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;border: 1px solid #c9cdd0;margin-left:100px;margin-bottom:15px;&quot; width=&quot;403px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Partnership programs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	We believe our Partners and importantly understand all their unique requirements in respect of successful development and growth along with our business.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Getting our Partner, you are integrated into our business so we&amp;rsquo;ll do our real best to develop your company &amp;nbsp;build together with our company.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Deciding a partnership agreement with Forexray, you get a properly secured positive benefit, excellent service as well as the benefits listed below:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;1.Our company&amp;#39;s service is extremely easy to sell.&lt;/strong&gt; Partners do not handle any problems by selling our service to their clients. We continually expand our service super quality, provide our company&amp;#39;s customers with a new product and services along with preserving consumers&amp;#39; motivation to work with us by means of various commitment programs.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;2.Thought-out and suitable Partner Personal Office&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Typically the overall performance of the Partner Office allows&amp;nbsp; truly easily control the Customer Portfolio, economical, economic indicators and to run your business.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;3.Deficiency of restrictions by commission fee accrual and payment&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Not like various other companies, we do not agree any restrictions by accruing commission rates to our company&amp;#39;s Partners. We collect and spend a commission fee in consideration of each and every transaction executed by a customer received by you regardless of its volumes.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;4.Lack of limitations by commission withdrawal:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; . It is possible to withdraw a commission at any time and in anywhere any amount.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; .There aren&amp;#39;t any restrictions associated to transaction time.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;.The quantity of commission getting built up depends only on customers&amp;#39; trading volume&amp;nbsp; and is not decided by a number of acquired clients, cus