	(96, 1, 'Introducing Brokers', 'Introducing Brokers', 'Introducing-Brokers', 'Introducing Brokers', 'Introducing Broker is fundamentally an entity (individual or group) that refers clients to forex brokers.A Forexray Introducing Broker (IB) partnership program', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Introducing Brokers:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	An Introducing Broker is fundamentally an entity (individual or group) that refers clients to forex brokers. The Forexray Introducing Broker (IB) partnership program is ideal for individuals and institutions who want to earn commission by leading new clients to Forexray. The commission idea we offer is highly competitive and is based on the trading activity of the clients that IBs refer to Forexray.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	All brokerage services are provided by Forexray,By permit for IBs to focus solely on their business and getting to commissions. Our IB program is totally free to join and can prove to be a profitable business; all you need is the willingness and motivation to introduce new clients to Forexray.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Broker&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376204798_1315211351_edeal.jpg&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-border-radius: 4px; -moz-border-radius: 4px; border-radius: 4px;-moz-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;box-shadow: 0px 12px 11px #8c7c7c;border: 1px solid #c9cdd0;margin-bottom:15px;&quot; title=&quot;Introducing-Brokers&quot; height=&quot;281&quot; width=&quot;650&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	Competitive and escalating commission program - the more clients you recommend, the greater your income potential&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&q