ents you have signed up. Down the line, once you have become an Introducing Broker for Forexray and produced in a larger number of Clients you can increase the size of your reward.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The flexibility of this strategy means that we set out favorably against other companies in the current market by significantly improving our representatives&amp;rsquo; profits without getting a negative impact on their Clients&amp;rsquo; trading costs.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	We are happy to see you on our website and wish you financial success and prosperity.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	You can contact our Partnership Department and ask any questions you are interested in:&lt;br /&gt;\n	&lt;img class=&quot;cur_img&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1379844511_1216806794_edeal.png&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: text-top;&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Email:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:partnership@forexray.com&quot; needshandler=&quot;needsHandler&quot;&gt;partnership@for&lt;wbr /&gt;exray.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.p-img-style{text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 20:57:57', 1, 1, '2014-03-24 07:31:44', '183.83.37.214'),
	(98, 1, 'Fund Managers', 'Fund Managers', 'Fund-Managers', 'Fund Managers', 'Fund Managers', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-weight: bold;color: #000580;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Fund Managers:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray being recognized as a market leader and a favorite amongst Fund Managers.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray supports institutional services for recognizing Fund managers and financial organizations. Whether, your business is exclusively trading Forex or you&amp;#39;re seeking to expand into this asset class, our many years of experience ensure that you will receive the facilities, excellent services and knowledge you want successfully manage your business.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	The leading and most desired platforms used by Fund Managers around the globe, giving you complete control to at the same time perform multiple accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Though forex trading looks easy initially, most of the traders end up losing the total capital over a period of time. Some may lose all the money in a few days, and some may take a year or two. We saw all the Forex Tsunamis in last 20 years and held up in this tough market.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Even though sometimes market gives us more than what we ask for, we advise our clients to think 50% to 100% profits per Annum. We suggest that our clients invest highest risk money and support withdrawing profits. We don&amp;#39;t accept our clients to send in morethan money once we found the trading.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Funds Guarantee or Assured returns&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Generally those who are new in the market or scam starssupportinvestment managers with capital guarant