font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Two respectable factors to trade Forex:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Very first is actually simplicity. Unlike the thousands of stocks that a fairness trader must study, there are only a few leading foreign currencies, and at any one day you will be doing a currency pair business of one currency for another. In fact, over 80% of FX trading is focused in pairs of just 6 currencies: U.S. Dollar, Euro, Yen, Pound Sterling, Swiss Frank and Australian Dollar&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	A second advantage of Forex trading is convenience. Trading is 24 / 5 and moves with the sun; the Asian market is followed by the European Market then the U.S. Marketplace and back to Asia, 24 hours a day besides on weekends. Somewhere in the world, someone is always trading Forex and so can you throughout trading hours that last from 22:00 GMT with Sunday to 22:00 GMT with Friday. This will be Forex trading suitable for U.S. investors who can only operate in the evenings when the significant equity exchanges are closed.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Add in the power of beginning with a small initial capital outlay, and you can remember why Forex is the choice of an expanding number of Online Trading Academy students who want to createquick with significant upside potential in their stock trading.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Forex Benefit:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Learn why this trading market is becoming a preferred amongst traders and investors alike. Learn about the positive aspects of trading, and how you can become a part of it.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Fundamental Forex Terms and conditions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Learn the terminology, and understand what the top Forex traders are talking regarding&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;The Entire world of Global Trading:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	A much more in depth overview of the worldwide trading market. In this lesson the main aspects that drive the market are discussed and different financial instruments are explained.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Trading Psychology:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	This particular important lesson is crucial for any trader. With an emphasis on the importance of emotional intelligence, this training covers how to deal with losses, and features tools to help maintain good psychological behavior.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-03-19 22:06:56', 1, 1, '2014-03-11 06:49:17', '183.83.37.214'),
