	(200, 1, 'Webmaster Affiliate Program', 'Webmaster Affiliate Program', 'Webmaster-Affiliate-Program', 'Webmaster Affiliate Program', 'Forexray webmaster affiliate program is an affiliate program which gives webmasters and website owners an excellent opportunity to receive commission.', '&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;Webmaster Affiliate Program (IB)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Forexray webmaster affiliate program is an affiliate program which gives webmasters and website owners an excellent opportunity to receive a high partner commission. If you are an owner of a website, which is intended for users interested in finance, investments and internet trading, then this affiliate program is the most suitable solution for you. You will receive partner commission by redirecting users from your website to the forexray website.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Webmaster affiliate program advantages:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;High commission rates;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Min Trade Point (MTP) equal spread for each instrument;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;An opportunity to create your own partner network;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Multiple levels of affiliate commission;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;No initial investment required;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Easy registration of a partner account;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; Detailed statistics on trade transactions;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Reports on partner commission;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;A wide choice of advertising materials;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Informational support by RoboForex.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	partnership with InstaForex will enable you to get main income from your web resource. Working with InstaForex, you are sure to enjoy the best partnership conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;The partnership with InstaForex gives you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp; 1.5 &amp;ndash; 5.3 pips from every trade &amp;ndash; the biggest reward among all brokers&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Comprehensive statistics of your affiliate link&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Instant commission crediting to your affiliate account&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Support of the Partnership Department specialists regarding all the aspects&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;Prospects of closer cooperation and higher remuneration for fruitful partnership&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;p-img-style&quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;pip commission from every trade of subpartner`s customers New&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;A few minutes after a simple registration procedure is passed, you will receive an affiliate link and banners to either place on your website or use on the internet. Shortly after the registration you will have a total control over the detailed statistics regarding your cooperation with InstaForex, which will enable you to monitor each time your affiliate link is visited and to supervise activities of a customer you attracted on InstaForex website.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are happy to see you on our website and wish you financial success and prosperity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	You can contact our Partnership Department and ask any questions you are interested in:&lt;br /&gt;\n	&lt;img height=&quot;16&quot; alt=&quot;email&quot; class=&quot;cur_img&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1379844511_1216806794_edeal.png&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: text-top;&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Email:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:partnership@forexray.com&quot; needshandler=&quot;needsHandler&quot;&gt;partnership@for&lt;wbr /&gt;exray.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.p-img-style{text-align: justify;background-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1381225720_183991173_fxray.png);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 10px 3px;padding-left: 32px;}&lt;/style&gt;', NULL, NULL, '1', '2013-09-19 11:22:16', 1, 1, '2014-03-22 08:13:17', '183.83.37.214'),
	(201, 1, 'Deposit/ Withdraw Funds', 'Deposit/ Withdraw Funds', 'Deposit-Withdraw-Funds', 'Deposit/ Withdraw Funds', 'FOREXRAY trading account, Determine the exact type of procedure. Once you reach the part you need, you will be transferred for processing Deposit/Withdraw.', '&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n.story table, .story th, .story td { vertical-align: top; }	&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	Here, you can start an FX trading account, Deposit/Withdraw funds to/from already existing FOREXRAY trading accounts.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	To make sure you Deposit/Withdraw&amp;nbsp; funds to/from an FOREXRAY trading account, Determine the exact type of procedure. Once you reach the part you need, you will be transferred to a secure transaction area for processing Deposit/Withdraw.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	To change FOREXRAY trading account settings, just like leverage size, personalized information, mobile phone password or your current PIN-code, please contact the technical support service using email: &lt;span style=&quot;color:#0000ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;support@forexray.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div id=&quot;VisaMasterCards&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;An easy option for making Deposit/Withdraw to an FOREXRAY trading account utilizing virtual prepaid cards selected in the national currency of your country.EXCARD - nominal commissions for payment, flexibility in transferring money and quality reliability of all transactions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Electronic and Digital Payment Methods:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;FOREXRAY methods Deposit/Withdraw&amp;nbsp; utilizing the following payment methods:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;gallery_view o_h&quot; style=&quot;overflow: hidden;&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;strong&gt;1) D