	(210, 1, 'sample-Management', 'sample-aboutus', 'sampleManagement', 'forexray,Mangement,forexray,team', 'forexray,about,forexray', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;background: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1383039757_1144859079_fxray.png) no-repeat;height: 50px;padding: 0;margin: 0;width: 400px;z-index:3;margin-left:-38px; &quot;&gt;\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	FOREXRAY is driving the mission to ensure best viable solutions with an international attain.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\n	All of our Management Team is a specialist team of finance, technologies, authorized, marketing and advertising and sales and profit experts dedicated to helping to make FOREXRAY is a leading financial organization. By simply responsible regarding the business strategic way of the company and in request of new business development, FOREXRAY is powered by the vision to make sure excellent financial services using a global reach.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;Management&quot; class=&quot;imagedropshadow&quot; span=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://forexray.com/uploads/1376169625_1550239397_edeal.jpg&quot; width=&quot;650&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;inner-divs&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;hr class=&quot;hrstyle&quot; /&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;bio-main row-fluid&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;details&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;h4&gt;\n				Ania William&lt;/h4&gt;\n			&lt;h5&gt;\n				Chief Executive Officer&lt;/h5&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;\n				Ania is responsible for the global management and operation of the company and with strategic planning on key issues of company operations.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n	&lt;hr class=&quot;hrstyle&quot; /&gt;\n	&lt;div class=&quot;bio-main row-fluid&quot;&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;details&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;h4&gt;\n				Daniel Ethan&lt;/h4&gt;\n			&lt;h5&gt;\n				Client Services Director&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;\