t;h5&gt;\n				Partnership Relations Department Head&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;div class=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;\n				Responsible for maintaining partner relationships, Maria oversees the development and operation of the partner network, With Company since 2010.&lt;/p&gt;\n		&lt;/div&gt;\n		&lt;hr class=&quot;hrstyle&quot; /&gt;\n	&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;!--\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Ania William&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Chief Executive Officer&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Ania is responsible for the global management and operation of the company and with strategic planning on key issues of company operations.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Daniel Ethan&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Client Services Director&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Looks after all FOREXRAY Client Service operations. Aligns the activities of the Premium Clients Department and the Compliance Department. Working with the company since 2011.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Thomson&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Chief Operations Officer&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Thomson &amp;nbsp;has a best track record and over 10 years&amp;rsquo; experience in currency trading, with an broad understanding of treasury and all associated technical issues, as well as a strong academic background in Accounting.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Brock Tyler&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Chief Business Development Officer&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	As Chief Business Development Officer, Tyler is responsible for new business development and the international growth of the company by overseeing expansion into new products and markets.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Kevin Gerardo&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Finance Department Head&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Deals with client account credit and debit transactions. With the company since 2010&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;directorhdiv&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;nameStyle&quot;&gt;\n		Maria Anastasiya&lt;/h2&gt;\n	&lt;p class=&quot;jobTitle&quot;&gt;\n		Partnership Relations Department Head&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n	Responsible for maintaining partner relationships, Maria oversees the development and operation of the partner network, With Company since 2010.&lt;/p&gt;\n--&gt;\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\n/* .jobTitle{\n       font-style:italic;\n       margin:0 !important;\n       padding:0 !important;\n      }\n.nameStyle{ font-family:tahoma,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:#ff6600;font-weight:bold; }\n.directorhdiv {\nbackground-image: url(http://forexray.com/uploads/1382009607_2097557655_fxray.png);\nborder-style: solid;\nborder-width: 1px;\nborder-color: #CCC;\n\nheight:auto;\npadding-top: 3px;\npadding-left: 5px;\n} \n\n*/\nbody{\n-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\nfont-smoothing: antialiased !important;\n}\n\n.imagedropshadow{\n	padding: 5px;\n	border: solid 1px #CCC;\n        -moz-box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #999;\n	-webkit-box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #999;\n        box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #999;\n} \n.inner-divs {\n    float: none; \n \n}\n\n.bio-main{\n        width: 100%;\n    }\n        \n.row-fluid {\n    width: 100%;\n}\n.row-fluid:before, .row-fluid:after {\ndisplay: table;\ncontent: &quot;&quot;;\nline-height: 0;\n}\n.row-fluid:after {\nclear: both;\n}\n.bio-main .details {\n        float: left;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-right: 1px solid #ddd;\n        margin-right: -1px;\n        width: 33%;\n        margin-bottom: 23px;\n            }\n.inner-